                    "body": "If we want to make this a useful feature request, {{CastOptions}} could allow passing a type factory ({{std::function<std::shared<DataType>>(const std::shared<DataType>&)}} instead of a fixed type instance, so that users can select the output type dynamically based on the input type. I'm not sure it's worth the hassle, though.",
